relevant_findings.HEENT: Pupils round and reactive to light and accommodation; no LAD; oropharynx clear, no exudates
relevant_findings.CV: Regular rate and rhythm; no murmurs/gallops/rubs
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally; no rales/crackles/rhonchi
relevant_findings.GI: Soft, tender to palpation in epigastric region; non-distended; no guarding/rebound
relevant_findings.extremities: No clubbing/cyanosis/edema; 2+ distal pulses; peripheral IV present
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented; CN II-XII intact; motor function globally
